      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit remains mechanically robust, with the double-VANOS system recently serviced and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. This is a visceral, analog machine optimized for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and chassis feedback.",
