    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously cared-for 2018 Lexus RX 350 in a sophisticated Atomic Silver finish. This vehicle has been a reliable companion, consistently serviced at the dealership with a full maintenance log available for review. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though it shows minor, expected road wear such as small stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin appointed in Parchment leather; the seats are supple and comfortable, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster from regular use. Every electronic feature, from the premium surround-sound system to the heated steering wheel and navigation, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the V6 engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly, providing the quiet, composed ride Lexus is known for. It sits on a set of premium Michelin tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, honest vehicle that perfectly balances luxury with everyday dependability.",
